    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in spectacular shape. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always kept in the garage and looks just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and is officially ready for its next adventure. You seriously won't find one cleaner than this. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
